    <ThingDef ParentName="ApparelArmorPowerBase">
        <defName>Apparel_NanoSkin</defName>
        <label>Fibre Skin Suit</label>
        <description>Thin nano technology skin. Not as durable as a full nano-suit, but compact enough fit under
            clothing and even a nano-suit. This armor is typically worn by the highest tier super soldiers under their
            suits or by high value targets, against assassination. Very expensive and rare, but speeds the wearer up,
            and boosts protection stats. Best worn under a nano-suit and reactive armor.</description>
